sentences: Benjamin David Goldberg (born September 24, 1998), known professionally as Token, is an American rapper and songwriter from Boston, Massachusetts.
In his younger years, Goldberg was being suspended from school for yelling at his teachers and fighting.
section: == Early life ==

sentences: He began rhyming and writing rap songs at 10 years old.
